plot: The tension remains between Heather and Shannon after their disagreement over seating arrangements at the holiday dinner outing. Meanwhile, Vicki continues to struggle with her daughter's decision to move to Oklahoma as Briana asks her to come along on a house-hunting trip. Heather hosts her closest friends and family for a hoedown-themed breaking ground party for their new house. Despite the festive mood, not all is calm at the Dubrow Ranch, and after taking a ride on the mechanical bull, one of the ladies ends up at urgent care.—Anonymous
